    "name": "Ultimate ADOM - Caverns of Chaos",
    "steam_appid": 1266820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/0cbf56bfee461410e9bea03956868461.avif?t=1728904390\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><strong>救世版</strong>的<strong>Ultimate ADOM – Caverns of Chaos</strong>，包含完整原声音轨和5张壁纸。购买救世版既可以支持开发者，也可以为公益事业做出一点贡献。<br><br>Assemble Entertainment将把<strong>救世版</strong>所获得的<strong>10%的收益</strong>捐助给<strong>国际癌症研究机构 (IARC)</strong>，以阻止腐败在游戏以外的世界蔓延！<br><br>加入我们，贡献你的力量吧，让我们一同拯救这个世界吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/3689e97b6fedd47c35b7798e01a0cfc6.avif?t=1728904390\" width=600 height=90 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >25年后，经典作品ADOM正式续作亮相</h2><strong>体验这款经过现代化改造的传统roguelike地牢攻略经典作品。无尽的程序生成地牢，蜂拥而至的敌人，嫁接系统，制造系统，庞大的技能树和物品让游戏有着无限的可重玩性。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深厚的背景故事</h2><br><br>邪恶已被击败，安卡蒂亚重获和平，人们再次燃起了发展的热情。七个各具特色的派系争夺着这片被安多·德拉克的遗灾蹂躏过的土地。而在某个邪恶的黑暗洞窟深处，混沌正蠢蠢欲动...<br>拿起你的宝剑，准备你的法术，磨砺你的匕首，拉紧你的长弓，因为你即将踏入不祥的混沌洞窟。小心选择你的派系，因为你不过是他们诸多手下中的一员。<br>不论是为荣耀和财富而战，为愈发凋零的正义而战，还是为光明，纯洁，甚至是混沌而战，你的每个选择都将在混沌洞窟改变历史。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/5412cb372008cdf57314fe097fa5c488.avif?t=1728904390\" width=600 height=141 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典ROGUELIKE加上现代功能</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 无尽的程序生成地牢，蜂拥而至的敌人，庞大的技能树和物品让游戏有着无限的可重玩性。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 可互动环境！推翻火盆，打开棺材，砸烂大门或者把它变成傀儡来为你服务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 现代画面模式和经典ASCII画面模式供您选择。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 本能式操作系统让你不再需要记忆上百个繁琐的按键操作。当然，我们也为想要这么做的玩家保留了这个功能。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/4d68b490d969a825c871c00b7a4a0d99.avif?t=1728904390\" width=600 height=90 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >首屈一指的复杂度和内容深度</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 职业，性别，种族和派系都将改变游戏方式和挑战。NPC将对你产生不同的态度，根据你的选择将解锁不同的任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 深邃的魔法系统，有着独一无二的魔法派系和超过八十种可选魔法 – 从召唤恶魔到活化地牢墙壁应有尽有，发挥你的想象力吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 超过二十五个技能树和许多隐藏技能树等待着你的解锁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 潜行系统为游戏开启了全新可能：不再踢门杀戮，而是遁影避战，攻敌不备！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 将敌人的肢体嫁接到自己身上，变成超级生化怪物。比拿两把剑更厉害的是什么？拿六把剑！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/f291eaba57b06f5a251073b74a747b00.webp?t=1728904390\" width=600 height=58 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >决不妥协的难度，惊险刺激的体验</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> 如何探索地牢完全取决于玩家。与对方交友，杀戮，深入亦或者平面勘探都可以选择。超过两百种需要不同手段应对的敌人在地牢中等待着你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/fafc7bdef20b0b5b2500535b063e3399.webp?t=1728904390\" width=16 height=20 /></span> &quot;死亡是乐趣的一环&quot; – 每次死亡都是永久的。但你的进展将会惠及未来的角色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266820/extras/f291eaba57b06f5a251073b74a747b00.webp?t=1728904390\" width=600 height=58 /></span>",
